sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy) 443/TCP
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant BFF as BFF Sidecar<br/>(e.g. Model Registry 8043)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Service<br/>(Model Registry, LlamaStack, etc.)

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 1: User Request Through Gateway to Dashboard
    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS reencrypt
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(projects.list permission)
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token<br/>x-forwarded-user
    Dashboard-->>KRBAC: React SPA + federation config
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTML/JS/CSS

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 2: K8s API Proxy Request
    Browser->>Gateway: POST /api/k8s/... (HTTPS/443)<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token>
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/6443<br/>Bearer Token passthrough
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: JSON response
    Dashboard-->>KRBAC: HTTP response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS
    Gateway-->>Browser: JSON response

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 3: Module Federation Plugin Loading
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /_mf/genAi/remoteEntry.js<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Dashboard->>BFF: HTTPS/8143 (TLS 1.3)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF-->>Dashboard: remoteEntry.js bundle
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Federated React module
    Note over Browser: Browser loads & renders<br/>federated component

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 4: BFF API Request (e.g. Model Registry)
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /_mf/modelRegistry/api/v1/...<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBAC: HTTPS/8443
    KRBAC->>Dashboard: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Dashboard->>BFF: HTTPS/8043 (TLS 1.3)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF->>Upstream: HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token
    Upstream-->>BFF: JSON response
    BFF-->>Dashboard: HTTPS response
    Dashboard-->>Browser: JSON response
